# AetherionAI-Mobile

Amonorepo with:

- **backend/**: Flask + SQLite API (Render-ready)
- **frontend/**: Expo React-Native + Web (Netlify-ready)
- **netlify.toml**: Netlify config
- **Procfile**: Render entrypoint
- **setup.sh**: quick-start script

## Quick Start

### 1. Clone & init
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/AetherionAI-Mobile.git
cd AetherionAI-Mobile
./setup.sh

cd backend
# edit .env as needed
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py

cd frontend
npm install
npm start      # Expo Go
npm run web    # Browser PWA
